0e61b94436ece5790db21415ddb6e5b96da557d9.query:
SELECT count(*) AS count 
            FROM recent_thanked
            WHERE user_id = $1 
            AND did_thank = $2
            AND at_time > $3

1a044b0aaffa9bc4d4db76cb23833aef50bbbe60.query:
SELECT user_id, times
        FROM thanked_users
        WHERE user_id != $1
        ORDER BY times DESC
        LIMIT 10

2f7c1c70132808e2f6cba543f9f9e8d56c25eafd.query:
INSERT INTO thanked_users (user_id, times)
                VALUES($1,1) 
                ON CONFLICT (user_id) 
                DO 
                UPDATE SET times = EXCLUDED.times + 1;
